{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1000,"text":"The stories we tell about each other"},{"time":3000,"text":"matter very much."},{"time":6000,"text":"The stories we tell ourselves about our own lives matter."},{"time":9000,"text":"And most of all,"},{"time":11000,"text":"I think the way that we participate in each other's stories"},{"time":13000,"text":"is of deep importance."},{"time":16000,"text":"I was six years old"},{"time":18000,"text":"when I first heard stories about the poor."},{"time":20000,"text":"Now I didn't hear those stories from the poor themselves,"},{"time":22000,"text":"I heard them from my Sunday school teacher"},{"time":25000,"text":"and Jesus, kind of via my Sunday school teacher."},{"time":28000,"text":"I remember learning that people who were poor"},{"time":31000,"text":"needed something material --"},{"time":33000,"text":"food, clothing, shelter -- that they didn't have."},{"time":35000,"text":"And I also was taught, coupled with that,"},{"time":38000,"text":"that it was my job -- this classroom full of five and six year-old children --"},{"time":41000,"text":"it was our job, apparently, to help."},{"time":43000,"text":"This is what Jesus asked of us."},{"time":45000,"text":"And then he said, \"What you do for the least of these, you do for me.\""},{"time":48000,"text":"Now I was pretty psyched."},{"time":50000,"text":"I was very eager to be useful in the world --"},{"time":52000,"text":"I think we all have that feeling."},{"time":54000,"text":"And also, it was kind of interesting that God needed help."},{"time":56000,"text":"That was news to me,"},{"time":58000,"text":"and it felt like it was a very important thing to get to participate in."}]},{"cues":[{"time":60000,"text":"But I also learned very soon thereafter"},{"time":62000,"text":"that Jesus also said, and I'm paraphrasing,"},{"time":64000,"text":"the poor would always be with us."},{"time":66000,"text":"This frustrated and confused me;"},{"time":68000,"text":"I felt like I had been just given a homework assignment"},{"time":70000,"text":"that I had to do, and I was excited to do,"},{"time":72000,"text":"but no matter what I would do, I would fail."},{"time":75000,"text":"So I felt confused, a little bit frustrated and angry,"},{"time":78000,"text":"like maybe I'd misunderstood something here."},{"time":80000,"text":"And I felt overwhelmed."},{"time":82000,"text":"And for the first time,"},{"time":84000,"text":"I began to fear this group of people"},{"time":86000,"text":"and to feel negative emotion towards a whole group of people."},{"time":89000,"text":"I imagined in my head, a kind of long line of individuals"},{"time":92000,"text":"that were never going away, that would always be with us."},{"time":94000,"text":"They were always going to ask me to help them and give them things,"},{"time":97000,"text":"which I was excited to do,"},{"time":99000,"text":"but I didn't know how it was going to work."},{"time":101000,"text":"And I didn't know what would happen when I ran out of things to give,"},{"time":106000,"text":"especially if the problem was never going away."},{"time":108000,"text":"In the years following,"},{"time":110000,"text":"the other stories I heard about the poor growing up"},{"time":112000,"text":"were no more positive."},{"time":114000,"text":"For example, I saw pictures and images"},{"time":117000,"text":"frequently of sadness and suffering."},{"time":119000,"text":"I heard about things that were going wrong in the lives of the poor."},{"time":122000,"text":"I heard about disease, I heard about war --"},{"time":124000,"text":"they always seemed to be kind of related."},{"time":126000,"text":"And in general,"},{"time":128000,"text":"I got this sort of idea"},{"time":130000,"text":"that the poor in the world lived lives"},{"time":132000,"text":"that were wrought with suffering and sadness,"},{"time":134000,"text":"devastation, hopelessness."}]},{"cues":[{"time":137000,"text":"And after a while, I developed what I think many of us do,"},{"time":139000,"text":"is this predictable response,"},{"time":141000,"text":"where I started to feel bad every time I heard about them."},{"time":144000,"text":"I started to feel guilty for my own relative wealth,"},{"time":147000,"text":"because I wasn't doing more, apparently, to make things better."},{"time":150000,"text":"And I even felt a sense of shame because of that."},{"time":153000,"text":"And so naturally,"},{"time":155000,"text":"I started to distance myself."},{"time":157000,"text":"I stopped listening to their stories"},{"time":159000,"text":"quite as closely as I had before."},{"time":161000,"text":"And I stopped expecting things to really change."},{"time":164000,"text":"Now I still gave -- on the outside it looked like I was still quite involved."},{"time":167000,"text":"I gave of my time and my money,"},{"time":169000,"text":"I gave when solutions were on sale."},{"time":171000,"text":"The cost of a cup of coffee can save a child's life, right."},{"time":173000,"text":"I mean who can argue with that?"},{"time":175000,"text":"I gave when I was cornered, when it was difficult to avoid"},{"time":178000,"text":"and I gave, in general, when the negative emotions built up enough"},{"time":181000,"text":"that I gave to relieve my own suffering,"},{"time":183000,"text":"not someone else's."},{"time":185000,"text":"The truth be told, I was giving out of that place,"},{"time":188000,"text":"not out of a genuine place of hope"},{"time":191000,"text":"and excitement to help and of generosity."},{"time":193000,"text":"It became a transaction for me,"},{"time":195000,"text":"became sort of a trade."},{"time":197000,"text":"I was purchasing something --"},{"time":199000,"text":"I was buying my right to go on with my day"},{"time":202000,"text":"and not necessarily be bothered by this bad news."},{"time":205000,"text":"And I think the way that we go through that sometimes"},{"time":208000,"text":"can, first of all,"},{"time":210000,"text":"disembody a group of people, individuals out there in the world."},{"time":213000,"text":"And it can also turn into a commodity,"},{"time":215000,"text":"which is a very scary thing."},{"time":217000,"text":"So as I did this, and as I think many of us do this,"},{"time":220000,"text":"we kind of buy our distance,"},{"time":222000,"text":"we kind of buy our right to go on with our day."},{"time":224000,"text":"I think that exchange can actually get in the way of the very thing that we want most."},{"time":227000,"text":"It can get in the way of our desire"},{"time":229000,"text":"to really be meaningful and useful in another person's life"},{"time":232000,"text":"and, in short to love."}]},{"cues":[{"time":235000,"text":"Thankfully, a few years ago, things shifted for me"},{"time":237000,"text":"because I heard this gentleman speak, Dr. Muhammad Yunus."},{"time":240000,"text":"I know many in the room probably know exactly who he is,"},{"time":243000,"text":"but to give the shorthand version"},{"time":245000,"text":"for any who have not heard him speak,"},{"time":247000,"text":"Dr. Yunus won the Nobel Peace Prize a few years ago"},{"time":249000,"text":"for his work pioneering modern microfinance."},{"time":252000,"text":"When I heard him speak, it was three years before that."},{"time":255000,"text":"But basically, microfinance -- if this is new to you as well --"},{"time":258000,"text":"think of that as financial services for the poor."},{"time":260000,"text":"Think of all the things you get at your bank"},{"time":262000,"text":"and imagine those products and services"},{"time":264000,"text":"tailored to the needs of someone living on a few dollars a day."},{"time":266000,"text":"Dr. Yunus shared his story,"},{"time":268000,"text":"explaining what that was,"},{"time":270000,"text":"and what he had done with his Grameen Bank."},{"time":272000,"text":"He also talked about, in particular, microlending,"},{"time":274000,"text":"which is a tiny loan"},{"time":276000,"text":"that could help someone start or grow a business."},{"time":278000,"text":"Now, when I heard him speak, it was exciting for a number of reasons."},{"time":281000,"text":"First and foremost, I learned about this new method of change in the world"},{"time":284000,"text":"that, for once, showed me, maybe,"},{"time":286000,"text":"a way to interact with someone"},{"time":288000,"text":"and to give, to share of a resource in a way that wasn't weird"},{"time":290000,"text":"and didn't make me feel bad --"},{"time":293000,"text":"that was exciting."},{"time":295000,"text":"But more importantly, he told stories about the poor"},{"time":298000,"text":"that were different than any stories I had heard before."},{"time":300000,"text":"In fact, those individuals he talked about who were poor was sort of a side note."},{"time":304000,"text":"He was talking about strong, smart,"},{"time":306000,"text":"hardworking entrepreneurs who woke up every day"},{"time":309000,"text":"and were doing things to make their lives and their family's lives better."},{"time":312000,"text":"All they needed to do that more quickly and to do it better"},{"time":315000,"text":"was a little bit of capital."},{"time":317000,"text":"It was an amazing sort of insight for me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":319000,"text":"And I, in fact, was so deeply moved by this --"},{"time":321000,"text":"it's hard to express now how much that affected me --"},{"time":324000,"text":"but I was so moved that I actually quit my job a few weeks later,"},{"time":327000,"text":"and I moved to East Africa"},{"time":329000,"text":"to try to see for myself what this was about."},{"time":331000,"text":"For the first time, actually, in a long time"},{"time":333000,"text":"I wanted to meet those individuals, I wanted to meet these entrepreneurs,"},{"time":336000,"text":"and see for myself what their lives were actually about."},{"time":339000,"text":"So I spent three months in Kenya, Uganda and Tanzania"},{"time":342000,"text":"interviewing entrepreneurs that had received 100 dollars"},{"time":344000,"text":"to start or grow a business."},{"time":346000,"text":"And in fact, through those interactions,"},{"time":348000,"text":"for the first time, I was starting to get to be friends"},{"time":350000,"text":"with some of those people in that big amorphous group out there"},{"time":353000,"text":"that was supposed to be far away."},{"time":356000,"text":"I was starting to be friends and get to know their personal stories."},{"time":359000,"text":"And over and over again,"},{"time":361000,"text":"as I interviewed them and spent my days with them,"},{"time":363000,"text":"I did hear stories of life change"},{"time":365000,"text":"and amazing little details of change."}]},{"cues":[{"time":367000,"text":"So I would hear from goat herders"},{"time":369000,"text":"who had used that money that they had received to buy a few more goats."},{"time":372000,"text":"Their business trajectory would change."},{"time":374000,"text":"They would make a little bit more money;"},{"time":376000,"text":"their standard of living"},{"time":378000,"text":"would shift and would get better."},{"time":380000,"text":"And they would make really interesting little adjustments in their lives,"},{"time":383000,"text":"like they would start to send their children to school."},{"time":385000,"text":"They might be able to buy mosquito nets."},{"time":387000,"text":"Maybe they could afford a lock for the door and feel secure."},{"time":390000,"text":"Maybe it was just that they could put sugar in their tea"},{"time":392000,"text":"and offer that to me when I came as their guest"},{"time":394000,"text":"and that made them feel proud."},{"time":396000,"text":"But there were these beautiful details, even if I talked to 20 goat herders in a row,"},{"time":399000,"text":"and some days that's what happened --"},{"time":401000,"text":"these beautiful details of life change"},{"time":403000,"text":"that were meaningful to them."},{"time":405000,"text":"That was another thing that really touched me."},{"time":407000,"text":"It was really humbling to see for the first time,"},{"time":409000,"text":"to really understand"},{"time":411000,"text":"that even if I could have taken a magic wand and fixed everything,"},{"time":414000,"text":"I probably would have gotten a lot wrong."},{"time":416000,"text":"Because the best way for people to change their lives"},{"time":419000,"text":"is for them to have control and to do that in a way that they believe is best for them."},{"time":422000,"text":"So I saw that and it was very humbling."}]},{"cues":[{"time":425000,"text":"Anyway, another interesting thing happened while I was there."},{"time":428000,"text":"I never once was asked for a donation,"},{"time":431000,"text":"which had kind of been my mode, right."},{"time":433000,"text":"There's poverty, you give money to help --"},{"time":435000,"text":"no one asked me for a donation."},{"time":437000,"text":"In fact, no one wanted me to feel bad for them at all."},{"time":440000,"text":"If anything, they just wanted to be able to do more of what they were doing already"},{"time":442000,"text":"and to build on their own capabilities."},{"time":444000,"text":"So what I did hear, once in a while,"},{"time":446000,"text":"was that people wanted a loan --"},{"time":448000,"text":"I thought that sounded very reasonable and really exciting."},{"time":451000,"text":"And by the way, I was a philosophy and poetry major in school,"},{"time":454000,"text":"so I didn't know the difference between profit and revenue when I went to East Africa."},{"time":457000,"text":"I just got this impression that the money would work."},{"time":460000,"text":"And my introduction to business"},{"time":462000,"text":"was in these $100 little infuses of capital."},{"time":465000,"text":"And I learned about profit and revenue, about leverage, all sorts of things,"},{"time":468000,"text":"from farmers, from seamstresses, from goat herders."},{"time":471000,"text":"So this idea"},{"time":473000,"text":"that these new stories of business and hope"},{"time":476000,"text":"might be shared with my friends and family,"},{"time":478000,"text":"and through that, maybe we could get some of the money that they needed"},{"time":482000,"text":"to be able to continue their businesses as loans,"},{"time":485000,"text":"that's this little idea that turned into Kiva."}]},{"cues":[{"time":487000,"text":"A few months later, I went back to Uganda"},{"time":489000,"text":"with a digital camera and a basic website"},{"time":492000,"text":"that my partner, Matthew, and I had kind of built,"},{"time":494000,"text":"and took pictures of seven of my new friends,"},{"time":497000,"text":"posted their stories, these stories of entrepreneurship, up on the website,"},{"time":501000,"text":"spammed friends and family and said, \"We think this is legal."},{"time":503000,"text":"Haven't heard back yet from SEC on all the details,"},{"time":506000,"text":"but do you say, do you want to help participate in this,"},{"time":508000,"text":"provide the money that they need?\""},{"time":510000,"text":"The money came in basically overnight."},{"time":512000,"text":"We sent it over to Uganda."},{"time":514000,"text":"And over the next six months, a beautiful thing happened;"},{"time":516000,"text":"the entrepreneurs received the money,"},{"time":518000,"text":"they were paid, and their businesses, in fact, grew,"},{"time":521000,"text":"and they were able to support themselves"},{"time":523000,"text":"and change the trajectory of their lives."},{"time":526000,"text":"In October of '05,"},{"time":528000,"text":"after those first seven loans were paid,"},{"time":530000,"text":"Matt and I took the word beta off of the site."},{"time":532000,"text":"We said, \"Our little experiment has been a success."},{"time":534000,"text":"Let's start for real.\" That was our official launch."},{"time":537000,"text":"And then that first year, October '05 through '06,"},{"time":539000,"text":"Kiva facilitated $500,000 in loans."},{"time":542000,"text":"The second year, it was a total of 15 million."},{"time":545000,"text":"The third year, the total was up to around 40."},{"time":547000,"text":"The fourth year, we were just short of 100."},{"time":549000,"text":"And today, less than five years in,"},{"time":551000,"text":"Kiva's facilitated"},{"time":553000,"text":"more than 150 million dollars, in little 25-dollar bits,"},{"time":556000,"text":"from lenders and entrepreneurs --"},{"time":558000,"text":"more than a million of those, collectively in 200 countries."}]},{"cues":[{"time":560000,"text":"So that's where Kiva is today, just to bring you right up to the present."},{"time":563000,"text":"And while those numbers and those statistics"},{"time":565000,"text":"are really fun to talk about and they're interesting,"},{"time":568000,"text":"to me, Kiva's really about stories."},{"time":571000,"text":"It's about retelling"},{"time":573000,"text":"the story of the poor,"},{"time":575000,"text":"and it's about giving ourselves"},{"time":577000,"text":"an opportunity to engage"},{"time":579000,"text":"that validates their dignity,"},{"time":581000,"text":"validates a partnership relationship,"},{"time":583000,"text":"not a relationship that's based"},{"time":585000,"text":"on the traditional sort of donor beneficiary"},{"time":588000,"text":"weirdness that can happen."},{"time":590000,"text":"But instead a relationship that can promote respect"},{"time":593000,"text":"and hope"},{"time":595000,"text":"and this optimism"},{"time":597000,"text":"that together we can move forward."},{"time":600000,"text":"So what I hope is that,"},{"time":602000,"text":"not only can the money keep flowing forth through Kiva --"},{"time":604000,"text":"that's a very positive and meaningful thing --"},{"time":606000,"text":"but I hope Kiva can blur those lines, like I said,"},{"time":608000,"text":"between the traditional rich and poor categories"},{"time":610000,"text":"that we're taught to see in the world,"},{"time":612000,"text":"this false dichotomy of us and them, have and have not."},{"time":615000,"text":"I hope that Kiva can blur those lines."},{"time":617000,"text":"Because as that happens,"},{"time":619000,"text":"I think we can feel free to interact"},{"time":621000,"text":"in a way that's more open, more just and more creative,"},{"time":624000,"text":"to engage with each other and to help each other."}]},{"cues":[{"time":627000,"text":"Imagine how you feel"},{"time":629000,"text":"when you see somebody on street who is begging"},{"time":632000,"text":"and you're about to approach them."},{"time":634000,"text":"Imagine how you feel;"},{"time":636000,"text":"and then imagine the difference when you might see somebody"},{"time":638000,"text":"who has a story of entrepreneurship and hard work"},{"time":641000,"text":"who wants to tell you about their business."},{"time":644000,"text":"Maybe they're smiling, and they want to talk to you about what they've done."},{"time":647000,"text":"Imagine if you're speaking with somebody"},{"time":649000,"text":"who's growing things and making them flourish,"},{"time":652000,"text":"somebody who's using their talents"},{"time":655000,"text":"to do something productive,"},{"time":657000,"text":"somebody who's built their own business from scratch,"},{"time":660000,"text":"someone who is surrounded by abundance,"},{"time":662000,"text":"not scarcity,"},{"time":664000,"text":"who's in fact creating abundance,"},{"time":666000,"text":"somebody with full hands with something to offer,"},{"time":669000,"text":"not empty hands"},{"time":671000,"text":"asking for you to give them something."},{"time":674000,"text":"Imagine if you could hear a story you didn't expect"},{"time":676000,"text":"of somebody who wakes up every day"},{"time":678000,"text":"and works very, very hard to make their life better."},{"time":681000,"text":"These stories can really change the way that we think about each other."},{"time":684000,"text":"And if we can catalyze"},{"time":686000,"text":"a supportive community to come around these individuals"},{"time":689000,"text":"and to participate in their story"},{"time":691000,"text":"by lending a little bit of money,"},{"time":693000,"text":"I think that can change the way we believe in each other"},{"time":695000,"text":"and each other's potential."}]},{"cues":[{"time":697000,"text":"Now for me, Kiva is just the beginning."},{"time":699000,"text":"And as I look forward to what is next,"},{"time":701000,"text":"it's been helpful to reflect on the things I've learned so far."},{"time":704000,"text":"The first one is, as I mentioned, entrepreneurship was a new idea to me."},{"time":707000,"text":"Kiva borrowers, as I interviewed them and got to know them over the last few years,"},{"time":710000,"text":"have taught me what entrepreneurship is."},{"time":712000,"text":"And I think, at its core, it's deciding that you want your life to be better."},{"time":715000,"text":"You see an opportunity"},{"time":717000,"text":"and you decide what you're going to do to try to seize that."},{"time":719000,"text":"In short, it's deciding that tomorrow can better than today"},{"time":721000,"text":"and going after that."},{"time":723000,"text":"Second thing that I've learned is that loans are a very interesting tool for connectivity."},{"time":726000,"text":"So they're not a donation."},{"time":728000,"text":"Yeah, maybe it doesn't sound that much different."},{"time":730000,"text":"But in fact, when you give something to someone"},{"time":732000,"text":"and they say, \"Thanks,\" and let you know how things go,"},{"time":734000,"text":"that's one thing."},{"time":736000,"text":"When you lend them money, and they slowly pay you back over time,"},{"time":739000,"text":"you have this excuse to have an ongoing dialogue."},{"time":741000,"text":"This continued attention -- this ongoing attention --"},{"time":743000,"text":"is a really big deal"},{"time":745000,"text":"to build different kinds of relationships among us."},{"time":748000,"text":"And then third, from what I've heard from the entrepreneurs I've gotten to know,"},{"time":751000,"text":"when all else is equal,"},{"time":753000,"text":"given the option to have just money to do what you need to do,"},{"time":756000,"text":"or money plus the support and encouragement"},{"time":759000,"text":"of a global community,"},{"time":761000,"text":"people choose the community plus the money."},{"time":763000,"text":"That's a much more meaningful combination, a more powerful combination."}]},{"cues":[{"time":766000,"text":"So with that in mind, this particular incident"},{"time":768000,"text":"has led to the things that I'm working on now."},{"time":771000,"text":"I see entrepreneurs everywhere now, now that I'm tuned into this."},{"time":773000,"text":"And one thing that I've seen"},{"time":775000,"text":"is there are a lot of supportive communities that already exist in the world."},{"time":777000,"text":"With social networks,"},{"time":779000,"text":"it's an amazing way, growing the number of people that we all have around us"},{"time":782000,"text":"in our own supportive communities, rapidly."},{"time":785000,"text":"And so, as I have been thinking about this,"},{"time":787000,"text":"I've been wondering: how can we engage these supportive communities"},{"time":790000,"text":"to catalyze even more entrepreneurial ideas"},{"time":792000,"text":"and to catalyze all of us"},{"time":794000,"text":"to make tomorrow better than today?"},{"time":797000,"text":"As I've researched what's going on in the United States,"},{"time":799000,"text":"a few interesting little insights have come up."},{"time":801000,"text":"So one is that, of course, as we all might expect,"},{"time":804000,"text":"many small businesses in the U.S. and all over the world"},{"time":806000,"text":"still need money to grow and to do more of what they want to do"},{"time":809000,"text":"or they might need money during a hard month."},{"time":811000,"text":"But there's always a need for resources close by."},{"time":814000,"text":"Another thing is, it turns out,"},{"time":816000,"text":"those resources don't usually come from the places you might expect --"},{"time":819000,"text":"banks, venture capitalists,"},{"time":821000,"text":"other organizations and support structures --"},{"time":823000,"text":"they come from friends and family."},{"time":825000,"text":"Some statistics say 85 percent or more of funding for small businesses"},{"time":827000,"text":"comes from friends and family."},{"time":829000,"text":"That's around 130 billion dollars a year --"},{"time":831000,"text":"it's a lot."},{"time":833000,"text":"And third, so as people are doing this friends and family fundraising process,"},{"time":836000,"text":"it's very awkward, people don't know exactly what to ask for,"},{"time":838000,"text":"how to ask, what to promise in return,"},{"time":840000,"text":"even though they have the best of intentions"},{"time":842000,"text":"and want to thank those people that are supporting them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":845000,"text":"So to harness the power of these supportive communities in a new way"},{"time":848000,"text":"and to allow entrepreneurs to decide for themselves"},{"time":850000,"text":"exactly what that financial exchange should look like,"},{"time":852000,"text":"exactly what fits them and the people around them,"},{"time":855000,"text":"this week actually,"},{"time":857000,"text":"we're quietly doing a launch of Profounder,"},{"time":859000,"text":"which is a crowd funding platform for small businesses to raise what they need"},{"time":862000,"text":"through investments from their friends and family."},{"time":864000,"text":"And it's investments, not donations, not loans,"},{"time":866000,"text":"but investments that have a dynamic return."},{"time":868000,"text":"So the mapping of participating in the story,"},{"time":870000,"text":"it actually flows with the up and down."},{"time":872000,"text":"So in short, it's a do-it-yourself tool"},{"time":875000,"text":"for small businesses to raise these funds."},{"time":877000,"text":"And what you can do is go onto the site, create a profile,"},{"time":880000,"text":"create investment terms in a really easy way."},{"time":882000,"text":"We make it really, really simple for me"},{"time":884000,"text":"as well as anyone else who wants to use the site."},{"time":886000,"text":"And we allow entrepreneurs to share a percentage of their revenues."},{"time":888000,"text":"They can raise up to a million dollars"},{"time":890000,"text":"from an unlimited number of unaccredited, unsophisticated investors --"},{"time":893000,"text":"everyday people, heaven forbid --"},{"time":895000,"text":"and they can share those returns over time --"},{"time":897000,"text":"again, whatever terms they set."},{"time":899000,"text":"As investors choose to become involved"},{"time":901000,"text":"based on those terms,"},{"time":903000,"text":"they can either take their rewards back as cash,"},{"time":905000,"text":"or they can decide in advance"},{"time":907000,"text":"to give those returns away to a non-profit."},{"time":909000,"text":"So they can be a cash, or a cause, investor."},{"time":912000,"text":"It's my hope that this kind of tool can show anybody who has an idea"},{"time":915000,"text":"a path to go do what they want to do in the world"},{"time":917000,"text":"and to gather the people around them that they already have,"},{"time":919000,"text":"the people that know them best"},{"time":921000,"text":"and that love them and want to support them,"},{"time":923000,"text":"to gather them to make this happen."}]},{"cues":[{"time":925000,"text":"So that's what I'm working on now."},{"time":927000,"text":"And to close, I just want to say, look these are tools."},{"time":929000,"text":"Right now, Profounder's right at the very beginning,"},{"time":931000,"text":"and it's very palpable; it's very clear to me, that it's just a vessel, it's just a tool."},{"time":934000,"text":"What we need are for people to care, to actually go use it,"},{"time":937000,"text":"just like they've cared enough to use Kiva"},{"time":939000,"text":"to make those connections."},{"time":941000,"text":"But the good news is I don't think I need to stand here and convince you to care --"},{"time":943000,"text":"I'm not even going to try."},{"time":945000,"text":"I don't think, even though we often hear,"},{"time":947000,"text":"you know, hear the ethical and moral reasons,"},{"time":949000,"text":"the religious reasons,"},{"time":951000,"text":"\"Here's why caring and giving will make you happier.\""},{"time":954000,"text":"I don't think we need to be convinced of that. I think we know;"},{"time":957000,"text":"in fact, I think we know so much,"},{"time":959000,"text":"and it's such a reality"},{"time":961000,"text":"that we care so deeply,"},{"time":963000,"text":"that in fact, what usually stops us"},{"time":965000,"text":"is that we're afraid to try and to mess up,"},{"time":967000,"text":"because we care so very much about helping each other"},{"time":969000,"text":"and being meaningful in each other's lives."}]},{"cues":[{"time":972000,"text":"So what I think I can do today,"},{"time":975000,"text":"that best thing I can give you --"},{"time":977000,"text":"I've given you my story, which is the best I can do."},{"time":979000,"text":"And I think I can remind us that we do care."},{"time":982000,"text":"I think we all already know that."},{"time":984000,"text":"And I think we know that love is resilient enough"},{"time":987000,"text":"for us to get out there and try."},{"time":990000,"text":"Just a sec."}]},{"cues":[{"time":996000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":998000,"text":"Thanks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1000000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1010000,"text":"Thanks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1012000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1014000,"text":"For me, the best way to be inspired to try"},{"time":1017000,"text":"is to stop and to listen"},{"time":1019000,"text":"to someone else's story."},{"time":1021000,"text":"And I'm grateful that I've gotten to do that here at TED."},{"time":1024000,"text":"And I'm grateful that whenever I do that,"},{"time":1027000,"text":"guaranteed, I am inspired --"},{"time":1029000,"text":"I am inspired by the person I am listening to."},{"time":1032000,"text":"And I believe more and more every time I listen"},{"time":1035000,"text":"in that that person's potential to do great things in the world"},{"time":1038000,"text":"and in my own potential to maybe help."},{"time":1041000,"text":"And that --"},{"time":1043000,"text":"forget the tools, forget the moving around of resources --"},{"time":1045000,"text":"that stuff's easy."},{"time":1047000,"text":"Believing in each other,"},{"time":1049000,"text":"really being sure when push comes to shove"},{"time":1051000,"text":"that each one of us can do amazing things in the world,"},{"time":1054000,"text":"that is what can make our stories into love stories"},{"time":1057000,"text":"and our collective story"},{"time":1059000,"text":"into one that continually perpetuates hope"},{"time":1061000,"text":"and good things for all of us."},{"time":1063000,"text":"So that, this belief in each other,"},{"time":1065000,"text":"knowing that without a doubt"},{"time":1067000,"text":"and practicing that every day in whatever you do,"},{"time":1069000,"text":"that's what I believe will change the world and make tomorrow better than today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1072000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1074000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}